### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:9090/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Create task 1
POST http://127.0.0.1:9090/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy milk",
  "description": "Semi-skimmed, 2 litres"
}

###

### Create task 2 (no description)
POST http://127.0.0.1:9090/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Write unit tests"
}

###

### List all tasks
GET http://127.0.0.1:9090/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single task by ID (replace <id> with a real UUID from the responses above)
GET http://127.0.0.1:9090/api/tasks/<id>
Accept: application/json

###

### Update task — mark completed and change title
PUT http://127.0.0.1:9090/api/tasks/<id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy milk (done)",
  "completed": true
}

###

### Update task — description only
PUT http://127.0.0.1:9090/api/tasks/<id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description"
}

###

### Delete a task
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:9090/api/tasks/<id>

###

### Attempt to get a deleted / non-existent task (expect 404)
GET http://127.0.0.1:9090/api/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Attempt to create a task with an empty title (expect 400)
POST http://127.0.0.1:9090/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": ""
}

###
